# Tauri externalBin drop-in for the compiled agent-core sidecar.
#
# `npm run build:bin` inside agent-core/ produces
#   agent-core-<host-triple>[.exe]
# and places it here. This directory is referenced by
#   src-tauri/tauri.conf.json bundle.externalBin
# and by Tauri's build script — the binary MUST exist before `cargo build`
# even in a dev/check pass.
#
# `.gitignore` excludes the binaries themselves; only this README is tracked.
*
!.gitignore
!README.md
